Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.86,Black Signs,Book,0,0,0,,Посещаемость
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:09.57,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0,0,0,,Так, завтра начинаются летние каникулы!\NНе беситесь сильно. Всем ясно?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.10,Main-Takao,Такао,0,0,0,,Слышь,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.95,Main-Takao,Такао,0,0,0,,погнали завтра на пляж.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,А, давай.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.19,Main-Kimura,Кимура,0,0,0,,Мне, внезапно, захотелось арбуза!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,К чему бы это?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.08,Main-Takao,Такао,0,0,0,,Давайте плеваться семечками.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:28.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Давай-давай!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:12.91,Episode Title,Title1,0,0,0,,Велосипед\Nна Двоих
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,«Велосипед на двоих»
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.08,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Уже завтра каникулы.\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,О, да, Вот они, долгожданные каникулы!\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:28.16,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Никакой школы, можно играть сколько влезет!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.83,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Займись лучше домашкой.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:34.80,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,«Завтра только первый день каникул,\Nтак что можно забить», — так думал?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Как догадалась?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:37.88,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Значит, я права?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Н-Но ведь каникулы созданы для веселья.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:45.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Бассейн или, там, пляж. А ещё походы и всё такое.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.90,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Времени совсем в обрез!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Вот бы летние каникулы никогда не кончались!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Даже так?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,А мне нравится школа.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ведь…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,там весело.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.53,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Летние каникулы, да?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.42,Main-Nakai,Накай,0,0,0,,Жарень!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.65,Main-Mano,Мано,0,0,0,,Такой приятный ветерок.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.38,Main-Mano,Мано,0,0,0,,{«Подбавь газку, браток!»… нет, не так. «Накатика скорости, а» и так тоже плохо}Прибавь ещё скорости!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.44,Main-Nakai,Накай,0,0,0,,Не проси невозможного, я и так спёкся.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.84,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Жара…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.86,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Может и нам попробовать?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Э?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.97,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Естественно, ты за рулём.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Нет, ни за что!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Так ведь, машина может сбить. Опасно!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.99,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Здесь нет машин и это не общественная дорога.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Но ведь…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Что такое? Неужели застеснялся?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.17,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,К-Конечно же нет!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.38,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,А, значит просто не умеешь.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,О чём это ты? Вдвоём на велике проще простого же.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Но, всё таки, это опасно. Лучше не стоит.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.96,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Тогда пошли на пустырь.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.76,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Э?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Если не сможешь, с тебя сок.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.28,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Смотри же, Такаги-сан.\N Совместная езда - легкотня!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Стой, это не считается!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Я смогу!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.75,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,С тебя сок.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Погодь! Погодь!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Н-Неужели совместная езда такая трудная?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан, ты ведь держишь равновесие?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.28,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Держу, конечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.44,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Уверена?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.85,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Сижу как обычно.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.60,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Не едем мы только из-за тебя, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ведь, последний раз, когда меня так катали,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.55,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,мой партнёр плавно крутил педали.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Э-Э? Вот это да.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.90,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Подруга?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.61,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Не-а. Это была не девочка.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.25,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,А…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ещё раз. У меня почти получилось.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.51,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ах ты!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:08.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Сейчас-то получится!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:12.24,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Чёрт… И почему я так расстроился!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Да что это такое?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.80,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ты как-то стал агрессивнее?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Нифига не агрессинее!\NЯ просто не хочу покупать тебе сок!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:23.51,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Именно, я просто не хочу покупать ей сок.\NТолько и всего!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.35,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ого, поехали.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.31,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Знаешь, Нисиката,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,последний раз вот так меня катал
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,мой папа.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Э?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.25,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Мне, вроде как, было 4 годика.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.56,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Держи.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Спасибо.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Вкуснятина!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.17,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката, а ты не будешь?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.76,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,А, ну…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Да, я… это… обойдусь.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Нельзя говорить, что денег не хватает.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.40,Black Signs,Can,0,0,0,,Виноградный {День}Сидр {Ну, почти}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Будешь?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Нет… всё в порядке.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Опять начнёт затирать про непрямой поцелуй,\N чтоб поиздеваться!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.87,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Не обманывай себя. Попробуй.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Я, правда, не хочу.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Терпение.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.44,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Нужно выстоять.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.80,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Держи, иначе схватишь тепловой удар.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.39,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Э? М-Можно?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.19,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Угу,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,так ведь…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката, ты так стесняешься непрямого поцелуя.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Д-Да не в этом дело!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.78,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Правда чтоли?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Я-Я тебе говорю!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.63,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ж-Жарко-то как.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Спасибо за напиток.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.79,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,We won't be walking home\N from school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. It's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:20.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Придумала.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:25.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Starting from tomorrow, let's practice\N tandem riding here until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.67,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.33,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay. But not on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.85,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll just ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,If we're only riding here, there's\N no point in practicing, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.53,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,No, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:43.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.65,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Well, then! Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Summer vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.95,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I can't wait for summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.88,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You're saying that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.58,Episode Title,Title2,0,0,0,,Первый\NДень\NЛетних\NКаникул
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.74,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,«Первый день летних каникул»
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:09.44,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,To think it would rain on the first\N day of summer vacation…\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.88,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,My summer vacation plans are ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.92,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,It's just for a day. Who cares?\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.08,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,I was supposed to go to the pool today.\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.48,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,I'm never getting the time back!\N{\alpha&HFFF&}`{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:21.96,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.09,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.82,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Let's start our homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.03,Main-Mina,Мина&Санаэ,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.09,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.00,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you didn't bring your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.57,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,I told you we should do our homework since\N we can't do anything because of the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.44,Main-Mina,Мина&Санаэ,0,0,0,,I thought I misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.46,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:44.18,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Why do we have homework during\N summer vacation in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.95,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.91,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,We can't have a vacation during vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.16,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.41,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,But we do have homework,\Nso we have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:06.93,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez! Юкари-тян,\N quit doing your homework and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.77,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Doing your homework in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.16,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,reminds me of homework,\N and I can't enjoy myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.54,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Not my problem! \NYou {\i1}should{\i0} be reminded of homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.58,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,It's only the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.88,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Just forget about homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:26.10,Italics,Юкари,0,0,0,,That's typical of a person who will be\N crying with regret on August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.30,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:31.01,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna read manga, so there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.68,100 % Unrequited,Manga,0,0,0,,100% Unrequited Love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.52,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.54,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Юкари-тян…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.98,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Can we write our book report on manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.37,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.50,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Can you two just go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.87,Black Signs,Title3,0,0,0,,Test of Courage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.93,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,"Test of Courage."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Good, it stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wait, why am I happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.86,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Yeah, we made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:29.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Uh, n-no… It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.82,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Wow, so many puddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.91,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It really poured last night, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't recognize her for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:43.06,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I ran into her\N coincidentally a few times on our days off,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}but this is our first time meeting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.80,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be what people call a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no! That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.19,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're just practicing tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.60,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.68,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.07,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,We can't tandem ride in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:08.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:12.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I was planning to go out in the\N afternoon right after our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.62,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It's a pain to go back home, so will\N you hang out with me to kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Is this… a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, no, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:28.26,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I guess so. But someplace\N where there aren't many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:31.67,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no telling what our classmates\Nwould say if any of them saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Then… How about…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,A test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Perfect for summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Isn't it usually done at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I heard it's really dark in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.07,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Besides, people say there's a presence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,What presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:01.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,This tunnel goes straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,but a lot of cars crashed into\N the walls for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,so they had to make a new\N road beside it instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:15.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ever since, the bloodthirsty\N ghosts appear every night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.23,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,in search of cars to prey upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:23.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Around here, there's a rumor\N about being spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.14,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Sometimes, people suddenly disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.75,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.11,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.57,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,It's only noon right now.\N There's no way I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's… way darker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}The breeze is making an odd noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.30,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Hey, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.26,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,A paper talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It's to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:03.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,That must mean there's something evil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not! That was only—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.65,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Look…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.74,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,What's this steel barrel doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.27,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Check what's inside, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.16,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.12,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I'm not scared! I'll look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I'll check it out, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,What's the big idea, Такаги-сан—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.67,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Quit messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:15.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't she say something about…\N being spirited away… or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:18.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.05,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.48,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Why are you screaming? It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:36.21,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You were looking for me just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that what it looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:44.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you, Такаги-сан.\N This was what you were after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Hey, over there…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.18,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,There's a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.84,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Why don't you peek inside, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if I'm gonna fall for the same trick again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't mock me, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I-It's stuck! My hand's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.54,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}How's my acting ability, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it's your turn to be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.11,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан, it's like something's pulling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:10.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Help—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Ni-shi-ka-ta…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.87,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I found it lying on the ground over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I'm glad your hand came loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:30.24,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it. You just wait,\N Такаги-сан. I'll get you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.99,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're way too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.84,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,We're back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Damn… I couldn't retaliate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.55,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Onii-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:47.01,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Another couple is on a date in the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.09,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,Shush/ Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.31,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,She called it a "date."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,What the heck was she was talking about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.46,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,The test of courage was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Uh… yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,It's almost noon. We should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.66,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,We're going in there again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You scared, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.56,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I met my quota for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.35,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:38.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's summer vacation, yet I still have\Nas many push-ups to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:42.23,Independent Research,Title4,0,0,0,,Summer\NScience Project
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.82,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,"Summer Science Project."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.82,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Yeah, the consommé flavor is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.16,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,You're lying. Your're teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:51.70,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,No way. Mine's better than\N your kelp flavor, Санаэ-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.56,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,They both sound awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.58,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,There are so many flavors to choose from,\N so why in the world would you choose those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.29,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Your watermelon flavor is\N playing it too safe, Юкари-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.01,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,Take risks in life whilst young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.80,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Taking risks on popsicle flavors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.76,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Anyway, did you two decide on\N subjects for your science projects?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.89,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.35,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.52,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,What about you, Мина?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.22,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,I'm still thinking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.48,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Isn't there something easy to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.50,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Like, something I can finish in a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.38,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,You should do actual research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.78,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,How about an observation diary on a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:28.11,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Good idea! That sounds so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.98,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,They basically behave the same every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.44,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,so all I have to do is copy and paste\N and change the dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.83,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Write it by hand, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:40.33,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Besides, a dog's day consists\N of waking up, barking for a walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.71,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,barking to be fed, sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.88,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,barking for attention, and\N barking to be fed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.56,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Why bother doing research about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.63,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,You're such a stick-in-the-mud, Юкари-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.89,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,Well, she is the class president, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.80,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,She can't help it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.14,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.45,Italics,Юкари,0,0,0,,Damn these two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.62,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,In any case, are you guys doing your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.85,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.44,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.41,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,Just so you know,\Nyou're not copying my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.61,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:15.41,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,I'll do your independent\N research for you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.91,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,On a dog, right? No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:20.67,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,You say that now, but you're gonna\N end up sharing your answers with us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.42,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,She is the class president, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.52,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.33,Italics,Юкари,0,0,0,,Maybe I should do an observation diary on\N these two for my independent research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:31.84,Tap Water,Title5,0,0,0,,Water Tap
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:30.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,"Water Tap."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.48,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the worst day of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.44,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.06,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I overslept this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then I had a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:52.62,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's a good thing it happened on\N the day we're not practicing tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Такаги-сан said she's\N going on a family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was she coming back today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I put off going out during the day\N to help do chores around the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they still made me go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.62,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the worst summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just write that in my one-liner diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That looks like…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, I'm gonna follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:31.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I can find a\N weakness of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she… I think she saw me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, maybe it's my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}She noticed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can see your hat, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.35,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're trying to surprise me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time for a pre-emptive strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna write that in my one-liner diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-She got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.07,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Just grocery shopping…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.98,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,What a coincidence, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Let's go together. Tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Like I said, no tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.00,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Aww…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did she find out I was following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.17,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Then, let's walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch out, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.26,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, today is the worst day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:43.94,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.90,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ah, no. It's nothing. Just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:49.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,No, you should wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.24,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}How embarrassing…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.20,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Does it hurt that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:03.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,It's just that I was already having a bad day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.17,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,and now I got injured, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I was thinking this is the worst\N summer vacation ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:15.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez… What should I write\Nfor my diary homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:16.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:17.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Uh, it's gonna get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.14,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.49,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,That feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You tried to help me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.21,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.88,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You should come in, too.\N It's nice and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh? No…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Come in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.22,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Cools you down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:02.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I had a good summer vacation day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.14,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I got to see a certain somoene today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I'll hand you your souvenir tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop that, Такаги-сан, that's cold!
